description:
Christ Our Righteousness: Part 5. Do you need hope and encouragement? Then Steve Wohlberg's 6-part series about Jesus Christ OUR RIGHTEOUSNESS (see Jeremiah 23:5,6) is just for you! Watch Pastor Steve explain the Good News of Jesus, its vital connection to the Ten Commandments, its relationship to the Mark of the Beast, and how this message will lighten the earth (see Revelation 18:1) during Earths final crisis. Enlightening. Convicting. Converting. Inspiring.
